other_tests.findings: Generalized osteopenia, Wormian bones, several lateral rib fractures with callus formation, acute oblique right humerus fracture, and bowing and thickening of the bilateral femurs. The section of long bone shows a markedly thin cortex with hypercellular woven bony trabeculae. Healing fractures show irregularly arranged trabeculae with callus formation of woven bone and cartilaginous proliferation.
